{"tid":783159,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"【有圖】耶路撒冷宗教遊記(無信仰人仕) 加有感而發作左首歌","createTime":"2018-08-17T10:32:53.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-17T10:32:53.000Z","uid":201078,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"7bb6b418b2690f3cdbdeed0720c6d6270b67d673","tid":783159,"uid":201078,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-17T10:32:53.000Z","msg":"遊記<br />\n<br />\n以色列係一個好特別既地方，尤其係耶路撒冷就擁有住好濃厚既宗教色彩。<br />\n一抵步時，已經有好多猶太人著住佢地傳統既服飾，成身類似燕尾服，高身圓黑帽。<br />\n而我地緊係急不及待行去古城啦。<br />\n<br />\n古城分左4個區域，每個區域都屬於唔同既信仰﹕天主教 基督教 伊斯蘭教及東正教<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/17/182950_1e7e394c07aa8a3226abb0a51365e4c7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F17%2F182950_1e7e394c07aa8a3226abb0a51365e4c7.jpg&h=aadfb846&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我同友人一開始選擇行耶穌既受苦之路，雖然係短短既幾十分鐘，但如果係有信仰既人士必定感受好深<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/17/183000_7025fbd52098aa41c3780be6b1ab7a7e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F17%2F183000_7025fbd52098aa41c3780be6b1ab7a7e.jpg&h=171d4a52&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n古城面對住巴勒斯坦方向既山就係橄欖山，都係一個好值得去同好靚既地方(耶穌傳道)<br />\n<br />\n而由二月頭耶路撒冷一間hostel沖沖下涼既構思到而家出埋個Mv 係電台播到<br />\n全賴有一班朋友幫助先可以有完成品<br />\n呢首歌係我咁多首入面 最別樹風格 用左最多心機 想大家生活煩燥時 或者好chill禁一禁入去聽 認真推推推推推介<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=LZe9mK1ApBk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DLZe9mK1ApBk&d=bO0u9ZGjfLMWtTGwNArufDACEZ5EYDiH2DLr%2FNuFFp4%3D&h=2bca0499\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=LZe9mK1ApBk</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/17/183027_c13a19fbcb1debb2f89b9f4ad9d2284e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F17%2F183027_c13a19fbcb1debb2f89b9f4ad9d2284e.jpg&h=8197dc15&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/17/183029_8f2f4ed91746b01d2839951ccf07bb6a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F17%2F183029_8f2f4ed91746b01d2839951ccf07bb6a.jpg&h=920c67a9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/17/183032_f848572acf2a70e7baeaf856c118a040.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F17%2F183032_f848572acf2a70e7baeaf856c118a040.jpg&h=a0b9fb1d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/17/183035_5396973c0f6d117c5ea75c0a048f76f2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F17%2F183035_5396973c0f6d117c5ea75c0a048f76f2.jpg&h=0ef7111a&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}